lead_paragraph: Formula One world champion Lewis Hamilton was top of the timesheets in Russian Grand Prix practice on Friday after Mercedes team mate Nico Rosberg set the early pace and Ferrari suffered reliability problems.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Fastest in Russia, Vettel Stops
